data.description: Location-Location-Location! Welcome to your ideal Riverfront Retreat. This 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom Ranch Home on the Danvers River offers unobstructed views and a public launch for dingys, kayaks, jet ski's, etc. Enjoy one-level living (or add 2nd floor!) with hardwood floors beneath ALL the carpet. Feel the warmth of the heated bathroom floor on your feet.This home is saturated with sun through the bay window, heating up the rooms in the winter and welcoming the breezes of the river to cool off in the summer. The property features a 2-car garage with ample storage and a large deck for outdoor relaxation. Rubber roof only 10 years old, construction of home is 2x6. Fenced-in yard for added privacy for parties, cook-outs or just kicking back. Don't miss out on the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and stunning river views. Don't miss this chance to be by the water this summer!  No showings until the open house.
